The '''Galactic Republic General Ministry''' was the permanent [[Bureaucrat/Legends|bureaucracy]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. It had several responsibilities including supervising and providing financing for the [[General Ministry Institutes]], managing the [[General Ministry Communications Agency]], and, during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], directing the [[Victory Rationing Orders and Regulation Plan]].

